=== Scalars on --- line
from: @perlpunk
tags: anchor header scalar 1.3-err

Testing top level scalars with headers.

This would fail in 1.3 due to [[RFC 2]] which does not allow content on header
lines.

+++ in-yaml
--- "quoted
string"
--- &node foo

+++ in-json
"quoted string"
"foo"

+++ out-yaml
--- "quoted string"
--- &node foo
...

+++ test-event
+STR
+DOC ---
=VAL "quoted string
-DOC
+DOC ---
=VAL &node :foo
-DOC
-STR

